NK039(ti)034:1: // sh+r+ai ga na d+hi p+aa pa tsi ti bi d+h+aa
NK039(ti)034:2: na ma n+ma tha bi dza ya na bi ha
NK039(ti)034:4: dpal legs ldan tshogs kyi bdag po mchod pa'i cho ga bdud las rnam rgyal bzhugs so //
NK039(ti)034:5: kun bzang he ru ka dpal gdul ka'i 'gror //
NK039(ti)034:6: rjes chags gtum drag gar gyis rnam rol pa'i //
NK039(ti)034:7: rdo rje srin po legs ldan tshogs kyi bdag /
NK039(ti)034:8: rnal 'byor re skong bstan bsrung che la 'dud //
NK039(ti)034:9: de la 'dir dbang thob cing dam ldan gyi rnal 'byor pas /
NK039(ti)034:10: nyer dgu sogs dus gnyan la gnas khang bstar zhing spyan gzigs sna tshogs kyis brgyan /
NK039(ti)034:11: dam tshig gi bris sku sogs rten gyi mdun /
NK039(ti)034:12: thod snod la sogs pa'i nang du dam rdzas gtor
NK039(ti)034:13: ma sogs gzhung bzhin bshams nas mdun bskyed gsal gdab
NK039(ti)034:14: ni / bdag gi mdun gyi g.yon phyogs na rdo
NK039(ti)034:15: rje'i brag nag po ri rab lta bur de'i steng
NK039(ti)034:16: du zhing tshal pa dum bu /
NK039(ti)034:17: gson po gcal du bkram pa /
NK039(ti)034:18: dur khrod kyi sa gzhir mdung dang ral gri gshib pa'i pho brang /
NK039(ti)034:19: dbus gru gsum dang bcas pa /
NK039(ti)034:20: de'i nang du dgra bgegs kyi ro gan rkyal du yod pa /
NK039(ti)034:22: b+hurkura ma h+aa pad+ma d+he bur rtsi bur byi ke
NK039(ti)034:23: byi ma na so ho sho mo kro d+ha h'u
NK039(ti)034:25: b+hur kurma a prarna bud rtsi ke bi ma na
NK039(ti)034:26: se kha sho mog kro d+ha h'u h'u phata phata
NK039(ti)034:27: s+w+aa h+aa / b+hu ru ku ru i tsi ki byi tsush+ma kro d+ha h'u phata /
NK039(ti)034:29: ces bsnyen bsgrub bzhi'i sngags la lan gsum mam bdun brjod pas /
NK039(ti)034:30: dpal ye shes kyi mgon po legs ldan nag po zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
NK039(ti)034:32: dbu skra dmar ser me ltar 'bar ba /
NK039(ti)034:33: phyag g.yas g.yon gnyis kyis tsan+da gyi bing sngon po zur brgyad pa phyar thabs su bsnams pa /
NK039(ti)034:34: zhabs gnyis 'dor thabs su mdzad pa /
NK039(ti)034:35: sku la na bza' ljang nag ber chen mnab pa la /
NK039(ti)034:36: g.yung drung ris dang tshom bu ris kyis brgyan pa /
NK039(ti)034:38: gser skud dang rin po che'i ske rag bcings pa /
NK039(ti)034:39: zhabs la sag ti'i lhwam po che mnabs pa /
NK039(ti)034:40: dar gyi cod pan 'phur lce ngang ldan pa /
NK039(ti)034:41: ral pa gyen du bardzesa pa la dar nag gi thod kyis dkris pa /
NK039(ti)034:42: thod pas brgyan pa 'jigs par byed pa zhal gdangs ljag 'dril ba /
NK039(ti)034:45: zangs gri'i bing chung ngun sked la btsugs pa /
NK039(ti)034:47: ngang dkar smug gnyis phyir dkar /
NK039(ti)034:48: ber ljang ser gnyis phyi ljang /
NK039(ti)034:49: rgyab dmar nag gnyis phyi nag /
NK039(ti)034:51: de'i gru gsum gyi rgyab phyogs bzhi mtshams bzhi dang brgyad du /
NK039(ti)034:52: kro ta dz+wa la sa ma y+aa /
NK039(ti)034:53: rak+sha dz+wa la sa ma y+aa /
NK039(ti)034:54: yak+sha dz+wa la sa ma y+aa /
NK039(ti)034:55: tsit+ta dz+wa la sa ma y+aa /
NK039(ti)034:56: ma ma dz+wa la sa ma y+aa /
NK039(ti)034:57: zhes pas lha ma srin sde brgyad 'khor tshogs gtso
NK039(ti)034:58: bo dang 'dra ba phrag par sleb pa tsam brgyad
NK039(ti)034:59: bskyed do // de'i rgyab rang gi mdun gyi thad sor /
NK039(ti)034:60: yum kro ti shwa ri ma /
NK039(ti)034:64: de'i rgyab tu phyogs skyong bcu /
NK039(ti)034:66: de'i rgyab tu rta ba can gyi tshogs /
NK039(ti)034:67: de'i phyi rol du glang chen gyi tshogs /
NK039(ti)034:68: de'i phyi rol du rkang thang can gyi tshogs /
NK039(ti)034:69: de'i phyi rol du lha dmag bye ba dung phyur dang bcas pas bskor bar bsam la /
NK039(ti)034:70: gtso 'khor thams cad kyi spyi bor zla ba'i steng du dkar po /
NK039(ti)034:71: mgrin par pad+ma'i steng du +aahdamara po /
NK039(ti)034:72: thugs kar nyi ma'i steng du h'u sngon pos mtshan par gyur /
NK039(ti)034:73: de nas ye shes pa spyan drangs ba ni /
NK039(ti)034:75: e h+ya hi ma h+aa ka la dzahmh'u bam ho /
NK039(ti)034:76: ri ma la ya gnam lcags yod pa'i rtse mo
NK039(ti)034:77: nas ye shes kyi mgon po 'khor dang bcas pa
NK039(ti)034:78: spyan drangs la / sngar bskyed pa la gnyis su med par bstim zhing /
NK039(ti)034:82: dam brdar rnams rim pa bzhin bya ste /
NK039(ti)034:84: spos rol dbyangs 'gyu dang bcas pas /
NK039(ti)034:86: lang ka'i yul gyi grong rdal gyi //
NK039(ti)034:87: dbus kyi ri bo ma la ya //
NK039(ti)034:88: ko ka thang mar rgya mtsho'i do //
NK039(ti)034:89: drag shul yod pa'i rtse mo nas //
NK039(ti)034:90: dpal chen rdo rje srin po yis //
NK039(ti)034:91: bdud kyi sde rnams brtul nas kyang //
NK039(ti)034:92: gsang sngags 'khor lo bskor ba'i tshe //
NK039(ti)034:93: ming gi dbang bskur bran du khas blangs pa'i //
NK039(ti)034:94: rdo rje ro lang tshogs kyi bdag /
NK039(ti)034:95: mgon po nag po chen po dang //
NK039(ti)034:96: nye gnas kro ti shwa ri ma //
NK039(ti)034:97: yab yum gnyis su med pa'i 'khor //
NK039(ti)034:98: lang+ka'i bdag po la sogs pa'i //
NK039(ti)034:100: pho mo 'khor dang bcas pa rnams //
NK039(ti)034:101: 'dir gshegs mchod pa dam pa bzhes //
NK039(ti)034:102: mchod pa dam pa 'di bzhes la //
NK039(ti)034:103: bcol pa'i las rnams grub par mdzod //
NK039(ti)034:104: ma h+aa ka la ga na pa ti sa pa
NK039(ti)034:105: ri wa ra e a ra li hrim hrim dzahdzah
NK039(ti)034:106: sa ma ya s+t+wam tish+tha badz+ra /
NK039(ti)034:109: zhes bstims nas brtan par bsam mo //
NK039(ti)034:111: tshogs kyi bdag po ma h+aa ka la 'dus pa
NK039(ti)034:112: chen po'i rnal 'byor pho mo 'khor dang bcas pa
NK039(ti)034:113: rnams kyi zhal du ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta
NK039(ti)034:114: kh+aa hi / ma h+aa ba ling ta la kh+aa hi /
NK039(ti)034:115: ma h+aa rak+ta la kh+aa hi /
NK039(ti)034:116: ma h+aa tsit+ta la kh+aa hi /
NK039(ti)034:117: ma h+aa ba su ta la kh+aa hi /
NK039(ti)034:118: ma h+aa ko ro tsa na la kh+aa hi /
NK039(ti)034:121: d+hup+pe push+pe mam sa ma h+aa b+ha ling+ta pra ti dza ho /
NK039(ti)034:122: zhes gtor ma bstabs te mchod /
NK039(ti)034:123: tshogs bdag gis gtor ma dam rdzas longs spyod chang
NK039(ti)034:124: phud bdud rtsi ngang rak+ta'i mtsho zhal du gsol bar
NK039(ti)034:126: rdo rje can gyi rnal 'byor khyed //
NK039(ti)034:127: rdo rje can du ci nges na //
NK039(ti)034:128: gsang ba gsum gyis mnyam pa'i phyir //
NK039(ti)034:129: mi phyed rdo rje'i dam tshig 'di //
NK039(ti)034:130: gsang ba gsum gyi dbyings las byung //
NK039(ti)034:132: grub na 'jig pa'i dus med do //
NK039(ti)034:134: badz+ra a mri ta e h+ya hi sarba sman h'u h+r+aihth+aah zhes bdud rtsi gtor bas /
NK039(ti)034:135: tshogs bdag gi gnas su snying khar h'u /
NK039(ti)034:136: lce la +aah glad pa la thim pas /
NK039(ti)034:137: sku gsung thugs kyi dam tshig /
NK039(ti)034:138: phog pa las mi 'da' bar bsam /
NK039(ti)034:139: mi phyed gsang ba'i rnal 'byor pa //
NK039(ti)034:140: gnyis med don gyi dbyings nas byung //
NK039(ti)034:141: dbyings nyid mi 'jig rdo rje ste //
NK039(ti)034:143: gnyis su med par nan tan mdzod //
NK039(ti)034:146: zhes khos dam tshig khas blangs nas dam bca' bar bsam /
NK039(ti)034:147: de la dam tshig gi chu blud pa ni /
NK039(ti)034:148: kho ting nge 'dzin gyis gzer la /
NK039(ti)034:149: gsang ba gsum gyi dam pa rnams //
NK039(ti)034:150: khyed kyi rab tu bsrus gyur na //
NK039(ti)034:151: de kun khros nas khrag chen po //
NK039(ti)034:152: nyams pa'i snying nas drangs te 'thung //
NK039(ti)034:153: i dan ti na ra kan /
NK039(ti)034:157: rak+sha si tam pa ni badz+ra a mri ta tod ta kan /
NK039(ti)034:160: snying la thim nas yi ge h'u mthing nag gcig tu gsal ba de /
NK039(ti)034:161: khos dam ma nyams pas bdag gi grogs byas nas ye shes sems dpa' dang /
NK039(ti)034:162: nyams na badz+ra yak+sha lcags kyi sdig pa mgo dgu pa kho'i gnyen po byed par bsam /
NK039(ti)034:164: zhes bdud rtsi gtor bas mna' bsgag par bsam la /
NK039(ti)034:166: rdo rje dri yi bdud rtsi mchog /
NK039(ti)034:167: pany+tsa a mri ta dang sbyang /
NK039(ti)034:168: bsre ba'i mchod de srog gis snying //
NK039(ti)034:169: snying dang snying gi bu bya'o //
NK039(ti)034:170: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta sa ma ya +aah zhes bdag gis kyang lan gsum blang ngo //
NK039(ti)034:171: khos zos 'thungs nas dam la mi 'da' bar bdag gcig tu grogs byed par bsam /
NK039(ti)034:173: ma h+aa gling gi grub gnas su //
NK039(ti)034:174: rdo rje srin po'i spyan snga ru //
NK039(ti)034:175: ci ltar khas blangs dam bcas pa'i //
NK039(ti)034:176: dam tshig gnyen las ma 'da' cig /
NK039(ti)034:177: ma h+aa ka la sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK039(ti)034:180: tshogs kyi bdag po mthu bo che //
NK039(ti)034:181: bar snang khams su rgyu ba las //
NK039(ti)034:182: bcom ldan rdo rje srin po yis //
NK039(ti)034:183: lag tu rdo rje byin nas ni //
NK039(ti)034:184: mngag byed ces kyang btag pa ste //
NK039(ti)034:185: tshogs kyi bdag po chen po bskos //
NK039(ti)034:186: ma h+aa ka la mthu bo che //
NK039(ti)034:187: 'chang byed rdo rje phreng ba can //
NK039(ti)034:188: bdag gis bsnyen cing sgrub pa las //
NK039(ti)034:189: gzhung dang 'gal ba mthol zhing bshags //
NK039(ti)034:190: phrin las snyan du gsol ba yis //
NK039(ti)034:191: lha'i dgra bla chen por gsol btab nas //
NK039(ti)034:192: rnal 'byor yongs kyi pho nyar zhal 'ches shing //
NK039(ti)034:193: lha min dmag tshogs 'dul ba thugs dam can //
NK039(ti)034:194: bdag gi bcol pa'i phrin las grub par mdzod //
NK039(ti)034:195: dam nyams dgra bgegs myur du bsgral du gsol //
NK039(ti)034:196: rdo rje'i brag chen gdan stengs su //
NK039(ti)034:197: bsnyen pa'i tshul gyis bka' sdod pa //
NK039(ti)034:198: tsan+da dbyug pa sngon po yis //
NK039(ti)034:199: khams gsum rdul du brlag mdzad pa //
NK039(ti)034:200: khyed kyi thugs dam dus la babs /
NK039(ti)034:201: bdag gis dgra bgegs tshogs dang g.yul 'byed na //
NK039(ti)034:202: mgon dang dpal du khyod stsol cig /
NK039(ti)034:203: log 'dren dgra bgegs rdul du brlag mdzad pa /
NK039(ti)034:204: bdag gi rgyal kha 'phel bar mdzad du gsal //
NK039(ti)034:205: dam tshig dbang gis lus dang grib ma bzhin //
NK039(ti)034:207: dam nyams dgra bgegs myur du bsgral du gsol //
NK039(ti)034:208: tshogs bdag khyed kyi 'khor tshogs kyi //
NK039(ti)034:209: bka' nyan rnams kyis bdag la khram btab na //
NK039(ti)034:210: khram kha phyi zhing bzlog tu gsol //
NK039(ti)034:211: tshe dang rdzu 'phrul mthu dang mngon shes dngos grub stsol //
NK039(ti)034:212: zas nor chos kyi dngos grub rtsal du gsol //
NK039(ti)034:213: thugs dam dus la babs po sa ma y+aah zhes pas las bcol lo //
NK039(ti)034:214: de nas thal mo sbyar te smon lam btab pa ni /
NK039(ti)034:215: mgon po khyed mchod byin rlabs kyis //
NK039(ti)034:216: phyogs dang dus kun thams cad du //
NK039(ti)034:217: sems can legs don 'byor pa la //
NK039(ti)034:218: bgegs kyi rnam pa kun med shog /
NK039(ti)034:219: rta dang ba glang nor dang 'bru //
NK039(ti)034:220: bu tsha pha ma gnyen bshes rnams //
NK039(ti)034:221: dge zhing tshe ring nad med par //
NK039(ti)034:222: thams cad 'byor pa ldan par shog /
NK039(ti)034:223: 'gro la nyes med bde gyur nas //
NK039(ti)034:224: nad dang mu ge kun bral shog /
NK039(ti)034:225: rgyal po dge zhing bde ba dang //
NK039(ti)034:226: chos kyi yul 'khor skyong bar shog /
NK039(ti)034:227: bde bar gshegs pa'i bstan pa 'di //
NK039(ti)034:228: phyogs bcu kun tu dar ba dang //
NK039(ti)034:229: myur du sems can thams cad kyang //
NK039(ti)034:230: chos kyi snod du 'gyur bar shog /
NK039(ti)034:231: dge ba thams cad yongs bsngo zhing //
NK039(ti)034:232: mgon po khyed mchod byin rlabs kyis //
NK039(ti)034:233: bdag cag 'khor dang bcas pa rnams //
NK039(ti)034:234: longs spyod rnam gnyis rdzogs par shog /
NK039(ti)034:235: bdag kyang byang chub mchog thob shog /
NK039(ti)034:238: zhes brjod la gtor ma byang shar mtshams su bskyal lo //
NK039(ti)034:240: mgon po'i thugs kar nyi ma'i steng du h'u /
NK039(ti)034:241: de la bsnyen sgrub bzhi'i sngags kyis g.yas su bskor bar bsam la /
NK039(ti)034:243: b+hurkura ma h+aa pad+ma d+he bur rtsi bur byi ke
NK039(ti)034:244: byi ma na se e ho sho mo kro d+ha
NK039(ti)034:245: h'u h'u phata phata s+w+aa h+aa /
NK039(ti)034:247: b+hu kurma a prarna bud tsi ke bi ma na
NK039(ti)034:248: so kha sho mo ga kro d+ha h'u h'u phata
NK039(ti)034:249: phata s+w+aa h+aa / zhes nye bsnyen dang /
NK039(ti)034:250: b+hu ru ku ru i tsi ka byi u tsash+ma kro d+ha h'u phata /
NK039(ti)034:254: rang gi sngags bzlas pa'i 'od zer mgon po la phog pas mgon po'i thugs dam gyi rgyud bskul /
NK039(ti)034:255: des drag byed 'khor rnams bskul bas /
NK039(ti)034:256: rang gi srog snying ram bu'i tshul du brjod pas /
NK039(ti)034:257: srog snying sngags kyi tshul bdag la phul bas /
NK039(ti)034:258: ci bcol pa'i bka' nyan par bsams /
NK039(ti)034:259: rang gi ci 'dod pa'i las mgon pos sgrub par bsam /
NK039(ti)034:260: badz+ra kro d+ha dz+wa la sa ma ya h'u /
NK039(ti)034:261: badz+ra yak+sha dz+wa la sa ma ya h'u /
NK039(ti)034:262: badz+ra rak+sha dz+wa la sa ma ya h'u /
NK039(ti)034:263: badz+ra ma ma dz+wa la sa ma ya h'u /
NK039(ti)034:264: phatah ces 'khor rnam bzhi'i sngags so //
NK039(ti)034:265: de ltar gtso 'khor gyi sngags rnams go rim bzhin
NK039(ti)034:266: ci lcogs zlas shing 'dod pa'i don la gsol ba
NK039(ti)034:267: yang yang gdab mthar mchod bstod dngos bshags rjes bsdu
NK039(ti)034:269: de yang brten med na ye shes pa gshegs /
NK039(ti)034:270: dam tshig pa bsdu tsa na /
NK039(ti)034:271: h'u zhig tu gyur nas rang yi dam gyi thugs kar bstim par gsungs so //
NK039(ti)034:272: zhes legs ldan tshogs bdag mchod pa'i cho ga bdud
NK039(ti)034:273: las rnam rgyal zhes bya ba kahthoga pa pra dz+ny+aa
NK039(ti)034:274: seng ha'am dam pa rin po ches mdzad pa ltar
NK039(ti)034:275: chags su bkod pa re zhig rdzogs so //
NK039(ti)034:277: rgyal ba kun gyi bdag po rdo rje 'chang //
NK039(ti)034:278: bskal pa sngon nas ye sangs rgyas gyur kyang //
NK039(ti)034:279: gdul dka' 'dul phyir drag po'i sku ston pa //
NK039(ti)034:280: dpal ldan nag po che la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK039(ti)034:281: dur khrod sgrol ging 'jigs byed mgon po dang //
NK039(ti)034:282: dgyes bskyed yum chen kro d+hi shwa ri ma //
NK039(ti)034:283: mdo sgyu'i rig 'dzin brgyud pa'i tshogs rnams dang //
NK039(ti)034:284: khyad par rgyal ba gnyis pa kahthoga pa'i //
NK039(ti)034:285: spyan sngar bstan pa srung ba khas blangs bzhin //
NK039(ti)034:286: theg mchog snying po'i bshad sgrub spel mdzad pa'i //
NK039(ti)034:287: 'dus pa'i sde skyong bcol pa'i las rnams gyis //
NK039(ti)034:288: bdag kyang 'di nas byang chub ma thob par //
NK039(ti)034:289: tshe rabs srung mar lha mchod khyed bsten na //
NK039(ti)034:290: byang chub bar du las rnams grub par mdzod //
NK039(ti)034:291: sangs rgyas kun gyi snying rje khros pa'i gzugs //
NK039(ti)034:292: spyan ras gzigs dbang drag po he ru ka /
NK039(ti)034:293: gdug pa 'dul phyir mgon po nag por cher //
NK039(ti)034:294: yongs shar khams gsum dpa' bo de la 'dud //
NK039(ti)034:295: lha mchog khyod kyi rdo rje yis //
NK039(ti)034:296: ma rung drag po bdud sde'i dpung gi tshogs //
NK039(ti)034:297: mthar byed kla klo mi srun gdug pa kun //
NK039(ti)034:298: rmeg med zhi ba'i phrin las mdzad du gsol //
